90. Write a PHP program to open a text file and print all the data in it.
code:
<?php
$filename = "sample.txt";

// Check if file exists
if(file_exists($filename)) {
    // Open file in read mode
    $file = fopen($filename, "r");

    if($file) {
        echo "<h3>Contents of $filename:</h3>";
        
        // Read and print the entire file until end-of-file
        while(!feof($file)) {
            $line = fgets($file); // Read one line
            echo nl2br($line);    // Convert newline to <br> for HTML display
        }

        // Close the file
        fclose($file);
    } else {
        echo "Error: Unable to open the file.";
    }
} else {
    echo "Error: File does not exist.";
}
?>
